ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Attend seminars related to Chemical Biology. I would recommend this course, because it is extremely important for obtaining the most recent information in their field.
Provided good exposure to the research in Chemical Biology at Yale and through seminars.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Attending Seminars in Chemical Biology provided me with information about some of the most recent research in my field, especially research which was being done at Yale. I am sure that some of the information gained during seminars will be applied to my research in the future.
